    <item>
      <title>苹果为使用高端音频格式的音乐家提供奖励</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/apple-dangles-reward-for-musicians-to-use-high-end-audio-format</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司正在向艺术家和唱片公司提供激励措施，鼓励他们使用空间音频技术来制作音乐，让听众沉浸在声音中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/apple-dangles-reward-for-musicians-to-use-high-end-audio-format</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 14:07:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AT&T 与爱立信 140 亿美元的交易标志着开放网络的到来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/at-t-s-14-billion-ericsson-deal-signals-new-era-of-open-ran-networks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[AT&amp;T Inc. 选择爱立信对其庞大的移动网络进行 140 亿美元的改造，标志着灵活无线技术时代的到来，该技术有望为由两家公司主导的基础设施市场带来竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/at-t-s-14-billion-ericsson-deal-signals-new-era-of-open-ran-networks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 13:48:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bluebell 股价下跌 60% 呼吁对 Worldline 董事会进行改组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/bluebell-calls-for-worldline-board-shakeup-after-shares-drop-60</link>
      <description><![CDATA[激进投资者 Bluebell Capital Partners 呼吁法国支付公司 Worldline SA 改组董事会并更换董事长，以“恢复市场的信任”，此前该公司股价一天内暴跌近 60%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/bluebell-calls-for-worldline-board-shakeup-after-shares-drop-60</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 13:33:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
